article.headline: McLaughlin's 21 lead Northern Arizona over VMI 78-69
article.description: — Trenton McLaughlin had 21 points in Northern Arizona's 78-69 win over VMI on Saturday in the Arizona Tip-Off.
article.linkText: McLaughlin's 21 lead Northern Arizona over VMI 78-69
article.story: GLENDALE, Ariz. -- — Trenton McLaughlin had 21 points in Northern Arizona's 78-69 win over VMI on Saturday in the Arizona Tip-Off. McLaughlin added three steals for the Lumberjacks (2-3). Jayden Jackson scored 18 points while shooting 5 for 12 and 8 of 12 from the free throw line. Carson Basham was 6 of 10 shooting to finish with 13 points, while adding 10 rebounds. The Keydets (1-4) were led by Tyran Cook, who posted 20 points. Koree Cotton added 13 points and six rebounds for VMI. Stephen Olowoniyi also had 12 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
